name: Owl Hair Pins
description:
These hair pins hold a miniature version of the owls featured on the owl bags. Hand made and delicate, they are waiting to sit securely on your hair! :)

Each owl has a black bobby pin securely attached to the back, but since they are crafted by hand one by one, they should be handled with care.

Owls measure about 1X1 in.

This listing is for ONE owl hair pin. Please choose to your preference.

name: Owl Cellphone Bags
description:
These cute little owl bags come in three different styles:

-Green background, orange owl
-Aqua background, yellow owl
-Blue background, green owl

They measure approximately 5X6.5 inches and are made to hold no more than the weight of a cellphone. The bags are handmade and hand-stitched. 

Please let me know which style you'd like to purchase and the quantity.

name: Inspirational Bento Box #2
description:
This wooden box is divided into 7 compartments, making it the perfect bento box to fill with trinkets that will get you through the day with inspiration. 

(From left to right)

A sushi roll so you never lack food (materials: felt).

A necklace for beauty.

A charm ideal for necklaces and bracelets, equipped to hold a picture of a love in your life.

A swallow for freedom and direction of home.

Duo of potions (pink vial is for love, gold bottle is for fortune).

Trio of inspirational pots (1st - love, luck, hope. 2nd - stone for stability. 3rd - pizzazz).

A charm for your phone.

name: Unicorn Blood Necklace - Harry Potter
description:
Unicorn blood is known to give you energy when you are feeling weak. Carry this around your neck and you will never have to worry!

The contents of this vial are non-liquid. It is filled with a sheer ribbon spiraled upward, giving the effect of liquid silver.
